*_PRD.md
*_local.md
# docs/ holds private planning / design notes (project convention).
# `docs/**` recursively covers subdirectories like docs/plans/ — the
# prior `docs/*.md` only matched top-level markdown and leaked
# docs/plans/*.md and any SVG/PDF into `git status`. Keep the README
# exception so an opt-in public README can still be tracked.
docs/**
!docs/README.md

